Champions earn spots in the EHF Champions League, while cup winners qualify for the European League.

programme.title: Um Salal vs Al Arabi - Qatar Stars League 2025/26 - W14
programme.desc: The Qatari League is the official football league in Qatar. The league includes 12 teams.
